@startuml Protection Proxy

interface BankAccount {
    + withdraw(amount: double): void
    + getBalance(): double
}

class RealBankAccount implements BankAccount {
    - balance: double
    + withdraw(amount: double): void
    + getBalance(): double
}

class ProtectionProxy implements BankAccount {
    - realAccount: RealBankAccount
    - userRole: String
    + ProtectionProxy(account: RealBankAccount, role: String)
    + withdraw(amount: double): void
    + getBalance(): double
    - checkAccess(): boolean
}

note right: Controls access based on permissions
note right: Security checks before operations

ProtectionProxy *-- RealBankAccount
Client ..> ProtectionProxy : uses

@enduml
